OL,3,CCanadian PM to be 'welcomed home' to
OL,4,CIreland
OL,6,FCanadian Prime Minister Mark Carney
OL,7,Fwill begin a two-day visit to Ireland
OL,8,Fon Saturday.
OL,10,FMr Carney, accompanied by his wife
OL,11,FDiana Fox Carney, will carry out a
OL,12,Fseries of engagements in Dublin city
OL,13,Fand Co Mayo in the west of Ireland.
OL,15,FMr Carney is the grandson of Irish
OL,16,Femigrants who were born in Mayo and
OL,17,Fleft the country more than 100 years
OL,18,Fago for Canada.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
