OL,3,CCanadian PM to be 'welcomed home' to
OL,4,CIreland
OL,6,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin said: "I will
OL,7,Fbe honoured to welcome Prime Minister
OL,8,FCarney and his wife to Ireland. It
OL,9,Fwill be an excellent occasion to
OL,10,Fcelebrate and strengthen the bilateral
OL,11,Frelationship between Ireland and
OL,12,FCanada.
OL,14,F"The strategic economic partnership we
OL,15,Fare due to sign on this visit will map
OL,16,Fthe various strands in our
OL,17,Frelationship and how we can enhance
OL,18,Fthese in the years ahead.
OL,26,@nD@PrpnD@`OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
