CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781345185
OL,3,CCanadian PM to be 'welcomed home' to
OL,4,CIreland
OL,6,F"With such strong Irish heritage, it
OL,7,Fwill also be an opportunity for Prime
OL,8,FMinister Carney to celebrate and
OL,9,Fexplore his Irish heritage, and I know
OL,10,FMayo is looking forward to welcoming
OL,11,Fhim home."
OL,13,FIreland's Government has hailed the
OL,14,Fvisit as a "significant milestone" in
OL,15,Frelations between the two countries.
OL,17,FIt said Ireland and Canada enjoy deep
OL,18,Fhistorical ties, with 4.4 million
OL,19,FCanadians ` over 12% of the population
OL,20,F` claiming Irish heritage.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@JO]vD@LOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
