OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781345185
OL,3,CCanadian PM to be 'welcomed home' to
OL,4,CIreland
OL,6,FThe Government also says Canada
OL,7,Fcontributed to peace and
OL,8,Freconciliation on the island of
OL,9,FIreland.
OL,11,FMr Carney will meet Mr Martin on
OL,12,FSaturday when they will announce a new
OL,13,F"bilateral co-operation framework" on
OL,14,Ftrade and investment, life sciences,
OL,15,Fresearch and innovation, and security
OL,16,Fand defence.
OL,18,FCanadian investment in Ireland has
OL,19,Fincreased by 131% since 2016 while
OL,20,FIreland is now Canada's eighth largest
OL,21,Fforeign investor.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
