PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781345185
OL,3,CCanadian PM to be 'welcomed home' to
OL,4,CIreland
OL,6,FThe visit also comes after the
OL,7,FOireachtas passed the Arbitration
OL,8,FAmendment Act, which enables Ireland
OL,9,Fto proceed to ratify the comprehensive
OL,10,Feconomic and trade agreement (Ceta)
OL,11,Fonce the legislation is signed by the
OL,12,FPresident.
OL,14,FThe visit will include an official
OL,15,Fdinner at Dublin Castle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
